snippet.title: Best VGM 840 - Halo 3 ODST - Bits and Pieces (Short Version)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1921 - https://youtu.be/fXxbFMtx0Bo

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360
Halo 3 ODST (2009)
Bits and Pieces (Short Version)
Martin O'Donnell & Michael Salvatori
